0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T15:04:59.000Z","msg":"00 至少最尾係和平<br />\n全人類同心恊力🤛🏻"},{"pid":"75fc11c3df7ab3728c9fcd07d41d935dc8d9a6b3","tid":349401,"uid":33162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T15:05:51.000Z","msg":"PD<br />\n打撚柒號角班仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee8076b639781495f920944ae97f6e16d8f4d238","tid":349401,"uid":35373,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T15:14:47.000Z","msg":"U.C.(宇宙世紀):包括高達origin,0079,0080,08ms,0083,高達Z,ZZ,馬反,F91,V高達等等,另外,高達thunderbolt,Turn-A既C.C.同G復國既R.C.都計埋入去，係地球又比人扔垃圾落黎，殖民星又毒氣又恐襲，仲會比人笑女人名，要追殺條友幾十集先報到仇<br />\nF.C.(未來世紀):機動武鬥傳G高達，成個地球唔洗要<br />\nA.C.(後殖民紀元):高達W，捱到莉莉娜上台就掂<br />\nA.W.(戰後紀元):X高達，寫明戰後，唔洗多講<br />\nC.E.(宇宙紀元):seed,seed-d，殖民星又食核彈，地球又有反中子搞到能源問題，同另外兩套捱到結局就安全既比，呢套最難捱<br />\nA.D.(西曆紀年):高達00，發達國既人其實幾安全，科技又發達，呢度咁多個選擇入面最好，不過如果你有得二轉做變革者既話要小心外星人<br />\nP.D.(戰後):魔劍，係火星要做狗，地球還好，不過一路比強權統治住，如果唔係一流駕駛員又會比魔劍插<br />\n<br />\n結論：gbf"},{"pid":"4b12130f36e334f784367a0a0f286c27d9af7d08","tid":349401,"uid":96640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T15:21:26.000Z","msg":"CC同RC有人提<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f65a6494407773f3c205d3f78b9da800cdf469cb","tid":349401,"uid":96640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T15:22:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>CC同RC有人提<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n睇漏咗自<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2e3848e731898710cdd754236362add433d4a1f","tid":349401,"uid":96640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T15:27:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>CC同RC<span style=\"color: red;\">冇</span>人提<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n睇漏咗自<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.g